result.name: Tamjai Samgor

reviews.text: First time to this shop and you may miss it beacuse you need to go upstairs and look for the main door. Plenty of seats and nice environment. My Samgor spicy bowl was great.
Definitely fills you up with the portion size, you should try the spicy soup.
Cheap and convenient. The food is average.
Tried the beef mixian, the beef is like the cha chaan teng beef and it's quite weird coz I thought they supposed to use the hotpot beef. Anyway the noodle is good
It's also nice, but.. quite spice
